node.text: These 4 Teams of racers ran a race with only a 48HR Window, starting in Gulf Shores, making their way all the way down the panhandle and around Key West and back up to Jacksonville! Such an awesome experience filming the start with Hook’D and FWC! Thanks to Captains for Clean Water for sponsoring along with the Governor of Florida, Ron DeSantis !
